<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
     <style>
      h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
        line-height: 1;
        text-align: left;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #545454;
        font-size: 1.75em;
        text-align: left;
        margin-bottom: 0em;
        font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;
      }
      h2 {
        color: #545454;
        display:inline;
        font-size: 1.2em;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
        letter-spacing: 0;
        padding: .25em;
        text-align: left;
      }
      h3 {
        color: #545454;
        font-size: 1.15em;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
        letter-spacing: 0;
        line-height: 1em;
        margin-top: .25em;
        text-align: left;
      }
      h4 {
        color: #545454;
        font-size: 1em;
        letter-spacing: 0;
        line-height: .6em;
        text-align: left;
        font-weight: normal;
        font-style: italic;
        font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
      }
      h5 {
        color: #545454;
        font-size: .85em;
        letter-spacing: 0;
        line-height: .6em;
        text-align: left;
        font-weight: normal;
        font-style: italic;
        font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
      }
      p {
        color: #545454;
        font-size: 1.1em;
        line-height: 1.1em;
        font-weight: normal;
        font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
      }
      strong{
        font-size: 1.15em;
        font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
      }
      ol, ul, td {
        color: #545454;
        font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.1em;
        line-height: 25px;
      }
      a {
        color: gray;
        a:visited {
          color: gray;
        }
        a:hover {
          color: black;
          background: none;
          text-decoration: none;
        }
      }
      </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h3>Your weekly wrap-up from CityVocie!</h3>

    <h3>In the last week the following location has seen activity: </h3>
    <br>
    <h2><%= @property.name %></h2>
    <br>
    <hr>
    <p>For questions or comments email: southbend@codeforamerica.org<br><a href="http://cityvoiceapp.com">cityvoiceapp.com</a></p>
  </body>
</html>
